more than one time per second.
  Finally with "Divide" you divide 360 degrees of movement for the time, in this way you will get
an adjournament per second, and the hand will move itself each time of an angle which result from
the report by 360 and the time in seconds.
  The most expansive is the "Full Wise" mode, the others two are similar.
		


